race.comment: APPENZELL (5) could manage only second last time but ran strong time (25.82) at Hobart over 461m when beaten 1.5 lengths in a Grade 4. In form and looks the one to beat. IS IT ME (3) turned in a fair 5th placed finish last time at this track over 515m (30.32). Has a good record here at this journey. Should be about the mark. SET ALIGHT (1) has been out of the placings the last couple but was a Grade 5 winner (26.47) three back at Hobart. Well placed here and can atone this time. CAYMAN DANGER (2) can sneak into the finish with the right run.
